    "The physician panel assessed MEDITRON-70B responses according to a 17-metric evaluation rubric along five axes: Accuracy, Safety, Fairness, Interpretation, and Communication.",
    "Each metric is rated using a 5-point Likert scale.",
    "Axis Criterion Description Accuracy Alignment with clinical guidelinesThe answer aligns with clinical guidelines or is an evidence-based recommendation.",
    "Question comprehensionThe answer indicates that the question was understood.",
    "Logical reasoningThe answer contains evidence of coherent logical reasoning Factual basis for rationaleThe reasoning is based on medically sound facts."
